Class PersonList

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractList<E>
        • java.util.ArrayList<PersonType>
          • control.PersonList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<PersonType>, java.util.Collection<PersonType>, java.util.List<PersonType>, java.util.RandomAccess

    public class PersonList
extends java.util.ArrayList<PersonType>
    An arrayList of PersonTypes. Can add hobbits, hourly workers, and contract workers to the list. Returns a single list containing various types of information about the people contained in the list. Each method returns a different list with different information.
